{"tid":332212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"住airbnb，隻鴿飛左入我間房痾屎，仲要唔肯走","createTime":"2017-07-22T21:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T15:31:31.000Z","uid":32932,"like":118,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd49d06c3e4fd291428ea163b974cb3e77c5b18","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/050124_098063a1f5cbe556bc5906de8abd2170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F050124_098063a1f5cbe556bc5906de8abd2170.jpg&h=4779128d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/050127_81f59e82ebca3cba7f50dbbe60868ef2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F050127_81f59e82ebca3cba7f50dbbe60868ef2.jpg&h=3e78f259&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/050128_7507a6a04427e6509084555fe2a96708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F050128_7507a6a04427e6509084555fe2a96708.jpg&h=9721de07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一入房，見到有隻雀嚇親。一開始以為係假雀，諗住咁別緻呀間airbnb，風扇上面仲有裝飾。最後見到佢眨眼先知原來係真雀。而家我同佢對峙緊，我望住佢，佢又望撚住我。<br />\n<br />\n隻死野應該入左我間房好耐，仲係我間房痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有冇痾喺我d行李上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街雀<br />\n<br />\n驚趕佢會係我間房亂痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後我d行李中晒招"},{"pid":"842c7ca374f4c2fec6184595d75e7ff43e86ec42","tid":332212,"uid":2419,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"好明顯係你霸左人間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0a589c88b2659cf9e7fd22f651a6b59c05fbf7","tid":332212,"uid":58911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:07:30.000Z","msg":"反映下啦 住幾多日先"},{"pid":"e3539062e6ef9b44384d291ec8264100d59aff8f","tid":332212,"uid":122438,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:09:23.000Z","msg":"你嚇到人瀨屎"},{"pid":"6ee089535f6c85f07fb8c2aedd5f01bc37d9c9c7","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反映下啦 住幾多日先</blockquote><br />\n訓左兩晚，今晚最後"},{"pid":"895838f8543a77da09767505a104b56a99bc80f5","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明顯係你霸左人間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會係間房既前主人"},{"pid":"bad3296bb6e6f6a1e51af48f93b89c315ba33c84","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:11:07.000Z","msg":"最嬲係我咁貴租間房，隻死野一蚊都冇畀過就霸左我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84e2f2e90ad058f86422802dfcd0b7b18360619","tid":332212,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:15:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77ea213d2c50b7629cdc18ac58fda7546a483292","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:19:44.000Z","msg":"我閂左房門，走之前同佢講：「我返黎之前你好快d走啦下。」但我再返去，佢都仲係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/051849_a1b1df2424013a9d7c23a9a750bb8079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F051849_a1b1df2424013a9d7c23a9a750bb8079.jpg&h=09531ff8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac314c8e6efa4ad18f0312f89038a83695b31c7","tid":332212,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995e5252faac66c2af94a4514a3bff78fb75f405","tid":332212,"uid":61653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:24:24.000Z","msg":"樓主咁撚毒人地都肯陪下你<br />\n仲想點丫"},{"pid":"da3973666a090145cdaab23ed6bbe4d17429e40a","tid":332212,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c243db5b77db461691cb1dc6706f2032f258311f","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咁撚毒人地都肯陪下你<br />\n仲想點丫</blockquote><br />\n咩呀 你講咩呀 出去隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b5408c345e7503115fad803f779e12cd304d59","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:32:42.000Z","msg":"airbnb host出左街 佢話佢地返緊黎 <br />\n搞到個host好唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我出街冇閂露台門窗先畀隻衰雀有機可乘 <br />\n佢地仲同我say sorry <br />\n好內疚 要人地仆返屋企同我搞雀"},{"pid":"8d0c501279a827370b81ecdf4193f7e827b17bff","tid":332212,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite